		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I had at least one Codemasters game (I don't have Micromachines unfortunately) where I remember there being a A/B select switch on the back of the cart.  I guess it was to disable/enable the lockout defeat.  On my toploader it worked fine in one mode, and didn't do anything in the other.  So maybe the board you have is permanently in the 'bad' mode?

		

