<br />
<br />
<br />
<br />Also, does it play any sound? Try to get some sound. Then the CHR ROM should be good and the RAM or mapper would need replaced, just to eliminate the problemed chips. <img src="./images/smilies/icon_smile.gif" alt=":)" title="Smile" />

		

